'''Charbi''' was one of the largest [[City/Legends|cities]] located on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Vulpter/Legends|Vulpter]]; it was considered a slum to most tourists. It was the location of the meeting arranged between [[Cal Omas]] and [[Dur Gejjen]].

